### Dapr Workflow — Orders example
### Compatible with VS Code REST Client and JetBrains HTTP Client.
### Run `make dev` first; the HTTP server listens on :8000 (port-forwarded by Tilt).

@host = http://localhost:8000

### 1. Schedule a new order workflow
# Captures the instance_id into the `start` request so the GET below can reuse it.
# @name start
POST {{host}}/v1/orders
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "item_name": "car",
  "total_cost": 15000.0
}

### 2. Poll the workflow status (uses the id from request #1)
GET {{host}}/v1/orders/{{start.response.body.instance_id}}

### 3. Poll a specific instance by id (paste manually if needed)
@instance_id = paste-id-here
GET {{host}}/v1/orders/{{instance_id}}
